      <talk_answer link_index="n277_bluff_dealers_pope-1-d" mid="107" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="106"><![CDATA[<html>$Dishonest Merchant Pero$<BR>Hehehe… But you can't find <FONT color=#a82424>Goddess's Tears</FONT> in any stage. Goddess's Tears are formed at the moment when the nightmare energy reaches its peak.</html>]]></talk_question>
